dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from an email from the IMO. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Fixed double space errors in 8 Senatorial District names.
DISCLAIMER: Dataset has Senatorial District attribution fields that are not standard for CODs but may be helpful for cartographic purposes. Admin p-codes do not include a Senatorial District p-code portion.
